{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in a place called Kwaadmechelen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that-- I-- [SIGHS] it was forced labor in-- in-- in a very soft way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lots of food, uh, freedom, uh, to walk around in the village, because Kwaadmechelen is a village.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Uh, there was a curfew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't go-- after a certain time, you couldn't leave your house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Uh, the only so-called guards was, uh-- I don't know how many people were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was 50, or 25, or whatever it was, usually families, OK?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was one-- one-- one or two people from the gendarmerie, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't mistreat us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just the opposite.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They just, uh--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there with my parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, 1900-- and, uh, let me see now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was 1941.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Malines was horrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Malines was the first taste of-- of being guarded by-- there were dogs down there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was SS down there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Uh, there were only men down there at the time that I was there, uh, which changed later on, because when the transport started in 1942, whole family came in.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was just like the, uh, the central point of-- of getting people together down there to send them somewhere else, which happened to be Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, uh-- but I learned a lesson.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Have you ever heard an ex-- expression to make yourself invisible, while looking at somebody and somebody looking at you?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I developed it to an art.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It's like one says, keep your nose clean.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's not really the same thing, but I, uh-- in German, you say-- you use the word [GERMAN], in other words, to be seen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, I choose to be-- not to be seen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Uh, I've never volunteered for anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
